---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="404 — Página no encontrada | Sibila">
  <div class="page-hero fade-up" style="min-height: 85vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding-top: 150px;">
    <div class="page-hero-eyebrow">Error 404</div>
    <h1><span data-lang="es">El aroma se ha<br><em>desvanecido.</em></span><span data-lang="en" style="display:none">The scent has<br><em>faded.</em></span></h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub" data-lang="es">La página que buscas no existe, ha sido movida o simplemente es un espejismo en el tiempo. Pero nuestro viaje sensorial continúa.</p>
    <p class="page-hero-sub" data-lang="en" style="display:none">The page you are looking for does not exist, has been moved, or is simply a mirage in time. But our sensory journey continues.</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 48px;">
        <a href="/" class="btn-primary" style="display: inline-flex;"><span data-es="Volver al Inicio" data-en="Back to Home">Volver al Inicio</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
